title: Smooth Criminal
tasting_notes: Rich chocolate, warm malt, and sweet caramel - a smooth and indulgent cup that's perfectly balanced

title: Seasonal Blend
tasting_notes: Smooth milk chocolate, crunchy roasted nuts, and luscious caramel for a rich, indulgent cup.

title: Beechworth Bold
tasting_notes: Deep dark toffee, smooth caramel, and luxurious chocolate. A robust yet velvety flavour profile.

title: Colombia (Single Origin)
tasting_notes: Bright lemon and berry acidity, rich coating body, and a smooth chocolate finish. Complex layers of floral, fruity, nutty, and sweet sugar tones.

title: Colombia Decaf (Single Origin)
tasting_notes: Rich cocoa powder, baked almond, and a touch of citrus zest. Smooth, balanced, and full of character.

title: Ethiopia Sidamo (Single Origin)
tasting_notes: Bright lemon and lavender, smooth vanilla sweetness, and juicy apricot. Balanced with refreshing lemon acidity and a finish of grapefruit and hazelnut.

title: Brazil (Single Origin)
tasting_notes: Milk chocolate and toasted hazelnut with crisp green apple highlights. Sweet berry acidity leads to a luscious caramel finish.
